      <header class="post-header">
        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
          从零开始Github Action:自动化驱动你的开发流程<span class="exturl post-edit-link" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2theWxlaC9rYXlsZWguZ2l0aHViLmlvMi9lZGl0L21hc3Rlci9zb3VyY2UvX3Bvc3RzL+WfuuS6jkdpdGh1Yi1BY3Rpb27pqbHliqjnmoRoZXhv6Ieq5Yqo5YyW6YOo572yLm1k" title="Edit this post"><i class="fa fa-pen-nib"></i></span>
        </h1>

        <div class="post-meta-container">
          <div class="post-meta">
    <span class="post-meta-item">
      <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
        <i class="far fa-calendar"></i>
      </span>
      <span class="post-meta-item-text">Posted on</span>

      <time title="Created: 2025-02-02 15:44:43" itemprop="dateCreated datePublished" datetime="2025-02-02T15:44:43+08:00">2025-02-02</time>
    </span>
